how-to-build boost for Hypertable
---------------------------------

1. download latest boost version from http://www.boost.org/users/download/
   or http://sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/boost/

2. unpack the package content (e.g. below boost_1_44_0/...) into this
   folder e.g. ...\hypertable\deps\boost\

3. run build-win32.bat or build-x64.bat

be patient wiht the build...
after successful build the intermediate files located in .\build\deps\boost could be deleted
